query: What are the model(s) of Lexus Ls (Xf40) with AWD drivetrain? Summarize the basic information of these models.
summary: The Lexus Ls (Xf40) with AWD drivetrain is available in three different models, the Ls 460 Awd, the Ls 460 L Awd and the Ls 600H. Both the Ls 460 Awd and the Ls 460 L Awd have 8-speed Aa80E AT transmission, 4.6L petrol V8 engine, and 1Ur-FSE engine code. They were produced between 2007-present and are available in North America. The LS 600H has a L110F CVT transmission, 5.0L hybrid V8 engine and 2Ur-FSE engine code. It was also produced from 2007 to present and is available in Asia and Europe region.

table.title: Tony Rickardsson - Speedway Grand Prix results

query: What is the relative progression of Tony Rickardsson's positions and points from 1995 to 2006 in the Speedway Grand Prix, and how did his best finish change during this period?
summary: Tony Rickardsson position in Speedway Grand Prix get much better from start of career, he begin in 2nd place in 1995 and then get 1st place in 1998, 1999, 2001, 2002, and 2005. His points also increase steady, from 88 points in 1995 to most high 196 points in 2005. About his best finish, at first he finish 2nd in some Grand Prix events in first few years, but after he get many 1st place as winner in different Grand Prix races in his career.

query: Summarize the medalists of the 50 Metre Rifle Prone in the year 1994.
summary: In 1994, the 50 Metre Rifle Prone was held in Milan. The gold medalist was Petra Horneber from Germany, the silver medalist was Beth Herzman from the United States, and the bronze medalist was Nieves Fernandez from Spain.

table.title: List of international cricket centuries by Adam Gilchrist - Test centuries

query: How does Adam Gilchrist's batting position influence his ability to score a century?
summary: Adam Gilchrist batting position seem to have big effect on his capacity to make century in international cricket. In table, we can see most of his century happened when he play at position 7, and there are few good play at positions 3, 5, 6, and 8. Because Gilchrist mainly played in lower middle-order, it looks like his capacity to make century is positively affected by his batting place, as it let him use foundation made by the top-order batsmen and score run in aggressive manner, and so, help his team to win.
